875
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:01,600
It's more convenient there.

876
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,200
Alright.

877
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,600
Then send it over as soon as possible.

878
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:06,880
Don't let this stuff distract him anymore.

879
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:07,760
Okay.

880
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,680
Sister Xin,

881
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:16,440
why do you look

882
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:18,200
a little unhappy?

883
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,120
I'm not.

884
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,520
I just feel

885
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,080
that Xiao Xing is such an adorable kid.

886
00:36:31,040 --> 00:36:32,360
You're missing having a child.

887
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,920
Mom, you're back!

888
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:39,800
You should've brought the kid along.

889
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,400
You are his mother, after all.

890
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,200
There's nothing I can do.

891
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,600
The court gave custody to his father.

892
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,800
I'll come back to see him often.

893
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,280
Sister Liang,

894
00:36:52,720 --> 00:36:55,680
you've cared for Dundun all these years.

895
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:58,640
You treat him like your own child.

896
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,400
Please take good care of him for me.

897
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,320
I know, I know.

898
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,360
Don't worry.

899
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:03,280
Thank you.

900
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:05,560
Thank you.

901
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:19,960
You're back.

902
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:20,920
All done?

903
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,200
Then hurry over to Xiaoling.

904
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:23,960
Try to settle everything in one go.

905
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,080
There won't be much time later.

906
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:25,680
I still have to attend

907
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:27,480
the Four Treasures Festival kickoff.

908
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:29,960
Come here.

909
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:30,960
What is it?

910
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:33,000
I saw in the group chat today

911
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:34,640
Peng put the Economic Development Office

912
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:36,360
in charge as the executive team

913
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,720
for the Four Treasures Festival prep.

914
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:42,320
Well, the executive team is just us two right now.

915
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,800
I'm the lead, you're the deputy.

916
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:46,760
Secretary Peng leads the steering group,

917
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,600
and Deputy Mayor Luo is the deputy leader.

918
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,800
Wait, wait, wait.

919
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:51,840
We're all bosses. Who does the work?

920
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:53,480
Everyone does.

921
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:55,720
Of course.

922
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:56,920
As for Secretary Peng,

923
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:59,040
he has to keep the town running normally.

924
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:00,760
Mainly it'll be

925
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:02,760
Deputy Mayor Luo

926
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,600
leading us on this.

927
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,200
Today,

928
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,480
all comrades present here

929
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:12,600
must be crystal clear on this:

930
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,640
Completing this task

931
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:17,320
concerns not only the next step

932
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:19,680
for Peach Blossom Town's Xuan paper trade,

933
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:22,480
but even more, the long-term future

934
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:24,160
of our entire Peach Blossom Town.

935
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,800
There's no room for slacking off.

936
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:28,600
Not the slightest carelessness allowed.

937
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:31,840
Director Lin,

938
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:33,760
why are you sitting way over there?

939
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,120
We've saved a seat for you right here.

940
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:35,840
Come on over.

941
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:36,640
No, no, no.

942
00:39:36,680 --> 00:39:37,320
Come on, come on.

943
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:43,280
You're Secretary Peng's handpicked lead.

944
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,880
The load on your shoulders is the heaviest,

945
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,520
and the challenges are the greatest.

946
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,280
I need you sitting next to me.

947
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,240
I'm afraid you'll flee at the last minute.

948
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:53,600
If you bolt,

949
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,240
all of us here

950
00:39:54,240 --> 00:39:55,320
would be totally finished.

951
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,400
As for the specific staffing arrangements,

952
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,920
Director Lin will go over them in detail shortly.

953
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:05,360
Departments must assign specific staff.

954
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:09,440
Later, submit the detailed name lists

955
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,320
and contact information

956
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:11,880
all to Director Lin.

957
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:13,280
Then everything, without exception,

958
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:15,920
will be under Director Lin's command.

959
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:16,760
Any problems?

960
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:17,640
No problem.

961
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:20,760
Deputy Mayor Luo,

962
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:24,280
