963
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,280
You're the one actually in charge.

964
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:29,480
Everyone should still follow your command.

965
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,600
If any problem arises,

966
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:31,800
Lin Yiran should also

967
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,360
report it to you,

968
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,600
and you'll handle it.

969
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:38,800
Old Liao,

970
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:42,920
you must delegate power to the young ones.

971
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,760
You have to trust their abilities.

972
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,080
Look, everyone.

973
00:40:47,680 --> 00:40:50,600
Security, fire safety,

974
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,720
including emergency medical care,

975
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,160
the county has specifically

976
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:56,400
set up a command center to handle it.

977
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:58,440
They've also set up a dedicated reception office

978
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:01,480
to handle visitors from all over.

979
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:03,120
So folks,

980
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:05,160
what's left for us?

981
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:07,680
Just the Xuan paper marketplace section,

982
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:10,360
organizing the booths and related matters?

983
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:13,760
Director Lin,

984
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,760
say a few words.

985
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:25,120
I just hope everyone can work together

986
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:27,920
to make the Four Treasures Festival a hit

987
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:30,840
and boost Peach Blossom Town's Xuan paper.

988
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:32,920
Director Liao here

989
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:35,240
