998
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:51,160
So in this report,

999
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:52,600
I emphasized two words:

1000
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:53,640
breaking out

1001
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,400
Expanding our circles

1002
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:57,080
from inside to outside the industry

1003
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:58,280
From the Four Treasures'

1004
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,840
makers, sellers, and users

1005
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,880
to various circles among young people

1006
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,480
attracting traffic from every circle

1007
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:06,520
So this Four Treasures Culture Festival

1008
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:09,640
will openly integrate tech, internet,

1009
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:11,680
and digital services for the first time

1010
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:14,280
with matching application scenarios.

1011
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:15,680
Our slogan this time is:

1012
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:18,680
Peach Blossom Town Four Treasures Festival

1013
00:42:19,160 --> 00:42:21,160
A shared festival for new creators

1014
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:33,800
This dish is delicious

1015
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:35,880
Director Liao

1016
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,520
You all take your time

1017
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:41,280
I'm done eating

1018
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,760
Me being a culture and tourism ambassador,

1019
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,360
here in Peach Blossom Town,

1020
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:48,080
is truly unprecedented

1021
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:51,200
I still don't know what I'm supposed to do

1022
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,680
Then you've got it wrong

1023
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:54,920
Many places have tourism ambassadors,

1024
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:57,000
